member.name: T:AFPST.Common.Web.WebUtilities
member.summary: Summary description for WebUtilities. Certain conventions must be followed for these functions to work properly. It is assumed that drop-down lists will use a data source with two columns of data, the first being the text of the list, the second being the value. It is also assumed that data grids will have a delete button as part of a template column, with the naming convention (datagridname)_delete. (If the data grid name is dg, then the delete button will be named dg_delete.)
